@node "Bugs" "Bugs, Ehhhhhhhh :("
@next "Bugs"
@prev "Bugs"

@{JCENTER}@{b}@{u}Bugs@{ub}@{uu}
@{JLEFT}
 · Idle A68K doesn't work correctly on V39/40 due to problems with the ClassAct/Reaction classes. Solution ? Upgrade !
 · Un-iconifying makes the window 8 pixels larger each time you do this. This is a bug in window.class V45, as V44 doesn't suffer from it.
   BTW: all Reaction programs have the same problem, afaik !!!
 · When using tooltypes/readargs WIDTH & HEIGHT you can't set below a certain value. However, you can do this afterwards, with the sizegadget.
   This is also a bug in the V45 window.class.

@endnode

