@node "Arexx" "The Arexx Interface"
@next "Arexx"
@prev "Arexx"

@{JCENTER}@{b}@{u}Arexx@{ub}@{uu}

Idle only knows a limited set of instructions, yet.
They are:

@{b}NAME@{ub} - name of idle 68k :)
@{b}VERSION@{ub} - version of idle 68k :))
@{b}AUTHOR@{ub} - my name :)))
@{b}IDLECOUNT@{ub} - how busy the system is, in percent.

If you wanna know how to include them, please take a look at the included example.

@endnode
